	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=230938><span id= >donkey</span></a><br><span id=notbold>2 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>People People People.<br><br>You are looking at the wrong history, the reason Eq has 1hB 2HB HP's etc is it is based on Gary Gygax's Dungeons &amp; Dragons not on the history of Medieval Warfare.&nbsp;&nbsp;What Gygax knew about swords, hammers etc their use and lethality could be written on a matchbox in large lettering.  Its a game not a history thesis and certainly not a simulation of anything at any time prior to Gary Gygax's D&amp;D 1st edition.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
